=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains information about an endpoint and port where client devices
can connect to an MQTT broker on a Greengrass core device.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 HostAddress => Str

The IP address or DNS address where client devices can connect to an
MQTT broker on the Greengrass core device.


=head2 Id => Str

An ID for the connectivity information.


=head2 Metadata => Str

Additional metadata to provide to client devices that connect to this
core device.


=head2 PortNumber => Int

The port where the MQTT broker operates on the core device. This port
is typically 8883, which is the default port for the MQTT broker
component that runs on core devices.



